==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: A greater man does not make note of a lesser man's faults.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dà rén bù jì xĭao rén gùo

===Phrase===
'''[[大人]][[不]][[计]][[小人]][[过]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') It is best to forgive and forget.

===Alternate forms===
[[大人]][[不]][[計]][[小人]][[過]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Related terms===
[[大人]][[不]][[记]][[小人]][[过]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

[[大人]][[不]][[記]][[小人]][[過]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

